org.apache.juneau.html

Enum AnchorText

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AnchorText>
      • org.apache.juneau.html.AnchorText
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<AnchorText>

    public enum AnchorText
extends Enum<AnchorText>
    Identifies possible values for the HtmlSerializer.HTML_uriAnchorText setting.
